<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī vijayābhyudaya śā 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>livāhana śaka varṣaṁbbulu 
<lb n="3"/>1712 yēṁḍlu cāṁdramānēna 
<lb n="4"/>sādhāraṇa nāma saṁvvatsara Āṣā 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḍha śu 15 lu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrī ciṁttakommadinne 
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> raṁlōnu Anaṁttapuramanē puṁ 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṇyastaḷamaṁdu vanāṁttarālu sama 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>sthamainaṣuvaṁṭi vṛkṣālu peddalu vēyi 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṁcci pālanacēśivuṁḍḍiri ganuka Āvṛkṣā 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>lu cāyanu tiruṇāla mahōtsavā 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>lalō samastamaina puṁṇyajanuluṁnnu 
<lb n="12"/>Ā chāyanu sakala sukhālatō vuṁ 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>duru ganuka Ā vanālalō vṛkṣālu 
<lb n="14"/>yavaru ganuka koṭṭēṭaṁduku <unclear>śe</unclear>lavu 
<lb n="15"/>yiccinavāruṁnnu Āvṛkṣālu koṭṭinavāru 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>nnu kāśilō gōhatya cēśinavāru 
<lb n="17"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> tṛ śiśu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="18"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> na pā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ya <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
</p>

